    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172040/extras/f62b21527ce1c70fe6c64694980983cd.poster.avif?t=1769595073\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172040/extras/f62b21527ce1c70fe6c64694980983cd.webm?t=1769595073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172040/extras/f62b21527ce1c70fe6c64694980983cd.mp4?t=1769595073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172040/extras/383178fce88f34b46dc924fd32b77f99.avif?t=1769595073\" width=600 height=99 /></span><br><strong>多层次战斗：</strong> 在《隐蔽之带》中，战斗发生在三层地图上，每层地图都为地面和飞行单位提供了战术挑战。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172040/extras/e3b9182c5076fd036e56d22624b9fe7e.poster.avif?t=1769595073\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172040/extras/e3b9182c5076fd036e56d22624b9fe7e.webm?t=1769595073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172040/extras/e3b9182c5076fd036e56d22624b9fe7e.mp4?t=1769595073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>爱丽舍疯狂：</strong> 魔法是你最强大的武器，也可能是你的毁灭。每次使用技能都会将你推向不可逆的边缘。用于魔法的爱丽舍力量会慢慢使你的英雄发疯，但也会赋予他们独特的力量。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172040/extras/eb09f88d17e1be3a45eac6ab7e728bfa.poster.avif?t=1769595073\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172040/extras/eb09f88d17e1be3a45eac6ab7e728bfa.webm?t=1769595073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172040/extras/eb09f88d17e1be3a45eac6ab7e728bfa.mp4?t=1769595073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>专长系统：</strong> 成功的战斗将使你的英雄变得更强大并学习新技能。灵活的专长系统允使你可以创造出独特而强大的英雄。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172040/extras/5ffae1fc855d1451fbffde356f6da125.avif?t=1769595073\" width=600 height=240 /></span>",
